## PROJECT OVERVIEW
Band Brain Hub is a single-page, mobile-critical web application designed for band members to collaboratively manage events, tasks, notes, finances, and setlists.  The application prioritizes rapid deployment, excellent UX/UI, and seamless real-time synchronization. Offline support is crucial.  The application is now implemented as a single-file application using React, and leveraging local storage for persistence.

## CODE STYLE
Consistent with standard React/Javascript best practices.  Emphasis on readability and maintainability.

