React, Javascript, HTML, CSS, Tailwind CSS, Font Awesome, uuid

## PROJECT-SPECIFIC STANDARDS
- All data is persisted locally in the browser's localStorage.
- The application is designed as a single-file application for ease of deployment and maintenance.
- UI should be intuitive for users with varying levels of technical expertise.
- The application should maintain a conversational tone in interactions with users.

## WORKFLOW & RELEASE RULES
